I installed this on Windows XP and it worked perfectly. I used it for months until switching to Windows 7.

So anyway, today I tried installing this on Windows 7 Ultimate 32 bit. It did NOT work. The mouse froze and I was getting no keyboard input. I had to restart, but when the Windows loaded again the system immediately froze up as it had before. I eventually had to go to safe mode to uninstall the thing.

So take my advice and don't install this on Windows 7 at all costs. The warning message at the start of the install claiming that it is not Windows 7 compatible should have been proof enough, but since no one here had commented I tested it out myself.

But for all you XP users, this is the best torrent to download. Like I said, I used it for months on XP with no problem.

Looks like I'm stuck without a decent firewall until someone uploads a newer version of ZA. :]
